content.rendered:
BOSS AIR OUTBACK AIRLOCKER PRO

Boss Air Outback Airlocker Pro available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

This kit is ideal to run air lockers plus have lots of air volume at hand for operating 4×4 tires, your buddies 4×4 tires, and his friends 4×4 tires, small air tools etc. Gives control over pressure to the air lockers to protect the seals, but leaves you with plenty of air volume for tools.

Includes

  • 1 x PX-07 3/4 hp 12 volt BOSS Air Compressor
  • 1 x AT-03 3 Gallon/ 9ltr Boss Aluminium Air Tank
  • 1 x 110-150psi Pressure Switch
  • 1 x 700mm Teflon Coated Stainless Steel Braided Hose
  • 1 x 100% Duty Solenoid
  • 1 x Check Valve
  • 1 x Flare Fitting
  • 1 x Drain Tap
  • 1 x 3/8” x 3/8”NPT push fitting for connecting your air line
  • 1 x Mini Regulator with Gauge for Air Locker Feed
  • 10 meters of 1/4” J844 DOT Airbrake line
  • 1 x 1/4” x 3/8”NPT fitting to connect air locker
  • 8 x Cable Ties
  • Instruction Sheet

Extra Options Available;

  • Remote Nitto Add-on
    • Add a remote Nitto Coupling so you can “plug-in” to pump up tyres or use air tools
To view the range of Boss Air products available, CLICK HERE!
Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
